			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>inflicts poison, and reduces their defense.<br>Also, immediately fills the skill gauge for<br>the user's second skill by 100%, then<br>gradually fills the skill gauges of the user's<br>first and second skills.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 644.8 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 967.2 × 1 hit<br>Special Effects:<br>・Defense -20%<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br>・Skill Charger (Skill 1)<br>　　Lasts 90 seconds<br>・Skill Charger (Skill 2)<br>　　Lasts 90 seconds<br>・Poison<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 58.2<br></div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
